#14 reset password to lock out legit user

Summary: In forgot password, it asks to enter email, and we do so, it says it resets the password and it will send the new password in email.
Steps to reproduce: Click on login, then Forgot password, then enter a email and click reset.
Impact: Due to this bug, an attacker can reset password of a legit user without their knowledge, and here most of the users created account using fake email. So it will cause permanent account lockout.
